Interface DescriptionOutput

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DataOutput
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ObjectDescription

    public interface DescriptionOutput
extends DataOutput
    An interface representing objects that support the same write operations as an ObjectDescription does. This is used to allow writing of descriptions to things other than ObjectDescription objects.
    Author:
    Alex Smith
